---
import CTAButton from "../ui/CTAButton.astro";
import NavigationHint from "../ui/NavigationHint.astro";
---

<!-- Solution Section -->
<section
  id="solution"
  class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-gray-800/50 relative"
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-16">
      Philosophic conversation
    </h2>
    <div class="prose prose-lg sm:prose-xl prose-invert max-w-none mb-16">
      <p class="text-xl text-center text-gray-300">
        While therapy addresses how you're faring and coaching focuses on
        performance, our specialty works with your natural response to what's
        important. Through conversation about what matters most, we help you
        hear your growth trajectory—where you've come from, what you're
        becoming, and what you're growing toward.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div
          class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-500/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-400"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Power listening</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300">
          I come not with advice but with generative questions and fortifying
          curiosity—helping you hear and say something important about what's
          important
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div
          class="w-16 h-16 bg-amber-500/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-8 h-8 text-amber-400"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Natural growth</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300">
          You respond to what's important by growing—it's your natural response
          and the only adequate response. When you hear what truly matters,
          growth happens naturally
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div
          class="w-16 h-16 bg-emerald-500/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-8 h-8 text-emerald-400"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Treasure the mind</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300">
          Your mind is infinitely rich—like an oil-rich country with unknown
          reserves. We take your thoughts seriously, setting aside devoted time
          with expert accompaniment to discover the wisdom that has yet to be
          articulated
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Let's talk CTA -->
    <div class="mt-8 text-center">
      <CTAButton variant="secondary" />
    </div>

    <NavigationHint href="#about" text="About Tam" />
  </div>
</section>
